{"title": "Final Campaign: Marines in the Victory on Okinawa", "description": "The three-month-long battle of Okinawa covered a 700-mile arc from\nFormosa to Kyushu and involved a million combatants--Americans,\nJapanese, British, and native Okinawans. With a magnitude that rivaled\nthe Normandy invasion the previous June, the battle of Okinawa was the\nbiggest and costliest single operation of the Pacific War. For each of\nits 82 days of combat, the battle would claim an average of 3,000 lives\nfrom the antagonists and the unfortunate non-combatants.\u201d (Joseph H. Alexander) ", "duration": 10901, "language": "English", "authors": [{"id": "15809", "name": "Joseph H. Alexander"}], "coverArt": "https://archive.org/download/okinawa_2103_librivox/finalcampaign_2103.jpg", "copyright_year": "1996", "genres": ["War & Military"], "supporters": [{"role": "Read by", "name": "Aaron Bennett"}, {"role": "Book Coordinator", "name": "Aaron Bennett"}, {"role": "Meta Coordinator", "name": "Lynne T"}, {"role": "Proof Listener", "name": "KevinS"}], "sections": [{"section": 1, "title": "The Final Campaign: Marines in the Victory on Okinawa", "readers": [14238], "path": "http://www.archive.org/download/okinawa_2103_librivox/tokinawa_01_alexander_64kb.mp3", "duration": 338}, {"section": 2, "title": "Countdown to 'Love-Day'", "readers": [14238], "path": "http://www.archive.org/download/okinawa_2103_librivox/tokinawa_02_alexander_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1279}, {"section": 3, "title": "Sidebars - The Senior Marine Commanders and The Japanese Forces", "readers": [14238], "path": "http://www.archive.org/download/okinawa_2103_librivox/tokinawa_03_alexander_64kb.mp3", "duration": 725}, {"section": 4, "title": "L-Day and Movement to Contact", "readers": [14238], "path": "http://www.archive.org/download/okinawa_2103_librivox/tokinawa_04_alexander_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1629}, {"section": 5, "title": "The Air and Sea Battles", "readers": [14238], "path": "http://www.archive.org/download/okinawa_